      <li>Full layer stack with blend modes and opacity</li>
      <li>18 color adjustments, 23 filters, 4 generators</li>
      <li>Rhai scripting API for batch automation</li>
      <li>Animated GIF and APNG import/export</li>
      <li>TIFF, JPEG, PNG, WebP, BMP file support</li>
    </ul>
